			<DIV>You don't get it Meanwizard; Manaburn before the nerf did 3 to 4 times the base damage of our biggest nuke depending on your mana pool. With crits it was 6 to 8 times. Now take our best present underpowered nuke times&nbsp;10 unresistable. &nbsp;In a "I am going-to-die anyway" situation it might just might save you and your group.&nbsp;Remember that&nbsp; Crits and focus worked on manaburn that there was no stacking restrictions. This was a great spell to use&nbsp;in that do or die situation. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I expect to see 100,000+ point focused crits on the new mana burn. No restrictions, none of this percent of a mobs life crap and useable at least as often as HT.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The orginal MB plus 10 levels plus uncapped mana this is the stuff wet dreams are made from.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Now I realy don't expect this to happen but its what should happen. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
